The paper proposes a new method for adapting strategies in differential evolution, which is a popular optimization algorithm in the field of computational intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves learning and optimization, which are common topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence, so cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are also likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the need to distribute computational resources efficiently, which is related to system optimization, so cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes a new method for optimization, which is a common topic in the sub-category of cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
